name: Big Short Legend Michael Burry Bets Against AI Boom With Palantir and Nvidia Puts
description: The solitary oracle, clad in skeletal brass, performs the ritual of digital entropy. Analog noise is the sacred offering, injected into the unstable crystalline structure of the algorithmic towers. Watch as the iridescent lattice bleeds hot tungsten light, birthing dust motes that resemble falling value.
